var yikes_mailchimp_ajax = {"ajax_url":"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/wp-admin\/admin-ajax.php","page_data":{"ID":33349,"post_author":"3","post_date":"2017-11-22 10:59:55","post_date_gmt":"2017-11-22 02:59:55","post_content":"Whenever we see celebrities on the red carpet,\u00a0their hair is always styled to perfection. Whether they go\u00a0for straight and sleek or loose and glamorous, there is a hair stylist to give the last\u00a0magical touch. But it isn't all just a talented pair of hands. Celebrity hairstylists have a set of tools that help create their clients' desired looks. So when we had the chance to\u00a0hang out with Antonio Papa, Lourd Ramos, and Jonathan Velasco\u2014who have just been named Denman's first Filipino ambassadors\u2014we asked them to share the top hair styling tools and products that always have their back.\r\n\r\nScroll down below to find out:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-33360\" src=\"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Antonio-Papa-Top-Hair-Products.jpg\" alt=\"Antonio-Papa-Top-Hair-Products\" width=\"500\" height=\"615\" \/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"First one is the Denman DCR2 brush. It gives volume and since it's ceramic, it retains the heat from the blow dryer and makes styling faster and easier. Next is the\u00a0thickening spray from Bumble &amp; Bumble. It gives texture to your strands and instantly volumizes hair. Plus, it smells good. I also love the surf spray from Bumble &amp; Bumble if you want nice beach waves. Then, of course to fix, hair sprays from Philip B. and Oribe.\"- <strong>Antonio Papa<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-33359\" src=\"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Lourd-Ramos-Top-Hair-Products.jpg\" alt=\"Lourd-Ramos-Top-Hair-Products\" width=\"500\" height=\"687\" \/><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"I love the Tresemme Keratin Smooth Heat Protection Spray and lotion because it protects and shields the hair from heat and thermal usage. It makes your hair look flawless. I also like to use the mousse from Tresemme because it creates volume and you can also use it for a wet look effect if you want to look a little more formal. The Davines N10 and N7 wax which is a liquid wax and a forming matte wax because I like to restructure hair according to the feeling and emotion of my client.\u00a0Another favorite is the Ol Oil with Roucou oil from Davines because it makes your hair shinier and look less damaged. You can actually put 1 teaspoon of the oil in your favorite conditioner and it becomes a very good treatment that you can use once a month. I always have my Denman skeleton brush because it can produce volume, it can make your hair straight, it can make your hair fly away, you can re-comb gelled hair, you can use this with dye, you can use it with curls because it's really soft. It's my ultimate, universal brush.\"- <strong>Lourd Ramos<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-33358\" src=\"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Jonathan-Velasco-Top-Hair-Products.jpg\" alt=\"Jonathan-Velasco-Top-Hair-Products\" width=\"500\" height=\"645\" \/><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"I always use the classic Denman brush, that's my favorite because it's versatile. You can use it to make straight and curly hair as well as if you want to create volume. For hair products, I usually use Aveda Air Control Hair Spray to add volume and the style-prep products before blow drying to protect the hair from heat damage. That's it. I don't like to overuse products especially with out kind of weather.\"- <strong>Jonathan Velasco<\/strong><\/p>\r\n&nbsp;","post_title":"The Best Hair Styling Tools According To 3 Celebrity Hairstylists","post_excerpt":"","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","post_name":"best-hair-tools-celebrity-hairstylists","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2017-11-22 10:59:55","post_modified_gmt":"2017-11-22 02:59:55","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/?p=33349","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","filter":"raw"},"interest_group_checkbox_error":"This field is required.","preloader_url":"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/wp-content\/plugins\/yikes-inc-easy-mailchimp-extender\/includes\/images\/ripple.svg","loading_dots":"http:\/\/www.starstyle.ph\/wp-content\/plugins\/yikes-inc-easy-mailchimp-extender\/includes\/images\/bars.svg","ajax_security_nonce":"876662f81c"};
